sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>OAuth2
    participant Notebook as Workbench Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>OAuth2 Proxy
    participant DSP as DSP API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>Bearer Token
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow<br/>Controller
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline Pod
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant ModelCtrl as ODH Model<br/>Controller
    participant ISVC as InferenceService<br/>Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>gRPC/REST
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Feast as Feast Online Store<br/>6566/TCP HTTP
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Workflow 1: Model Training to Deployment

    User->>Dashboard: Login via OpenShift OAuth
    Dashboard-->>User: Dashboard UI loaded

    User->>Dashboard: Create Notebook from template
    Dashboard->>Notebook: Create Notebook CR → StatefulSet
    Notebook-->>User: JupyterLab ready

    User->>Notebook: Develop & train model
    Notebook->>S3: Upload model artifacts<br/>PUT /bucket/model.pkl<br/>AWS IAM Auth
    S3-->>Notebook: 200 OK

    User->>Notebook: Create DSP pipeline YAML
    Notebook->>DSP: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Bearer Token<br/>Pipeline definition
    DSP-->>Notebook: Pipeline created

    User->>DSP: Submit pipeline run
    DSP->>Argo: Create Workflow CR
    Argo->>Pipeline: Launch pipeline pods

    Pipeline->>S3: Download model<br/>GET /bucket/model.pkl<br/>AWS IAM Auth
    S3-->>Pipeline: Model artifacts

    Pipeline->>KServe: Create InferenceService CR<br/>kubectl apply
    KServe->>ISVC: Create Deployment/Service
    KServe->>ModelCtrl: Notify ISVC creation
    ModelCtrl->>ISVC: Create Route, ServiceMonitor<br/>Inject EnvoyFilter

    Pipeline->>ModelReg: Register model metadata<br/>POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/model_versions<br/>Bearer Token
    ModelReg-->>Pipeline: Model registered

    Note over User,Prometheus: Workflow 2: Inference with Features & Monitoring

    User->>TrustyAI: Enable guardrails for ISVC<br/>Patch InferenceService
    TrustyAI->>ISVC: Inject guardrails orchestrator

    User->>ISVC: POST /v2/models/model:infer<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token (optional)<br/>Input data
    ISVC->>Feast: GET /get-online-features<br/>HTTP/6566<br/>Feature IDs
    Feast-->>ISVC: Feature vectors

    ISVC->>TrustyAI: Log request/response payload<br/>POST /info/inference/request
    TrustyAI-->>ISVC: ACK

    ISVC->>ISVC: Run inference<br/>model.predict(features + input)
    ISVC-->>User: JSON response<br/>Prediction result

    TrustyAI->>Prometheus: Export metrics<br/>GET /q/metrics<br/>bias_score, toxicity_score
    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: Scrape metrics

    Note over User,Prometheus: Workflow 3: Distributed Training

    User->>Notebook: Create PyTorchJob YAML<br/>import kubeflow.training
    Notebook->>KServe: Apply PyTorchJob CR<br/>kubectl apply
    KServe->>Pipeline: Create master + worker Pods<br/>Replicas: 1 master, 4 workers

    Pipeline->>S3: Download training data<br/>GET /bucket/dataset.parquet<br/>AWS IAM
    S3-->>Pipeline: Training dataset

    Pipeline->>Feast: GET /get-historical-features<br/>HTTP/8815<br/>Feature definitions
    Feast->>S3: Load feature data from offline store
    S3-->>Feast: Feature parquet files
    Feast-->>Pipeline: Historical features

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Distributed training<br/>torch.distributed<br/>Port 23456/TCP (inter-pod)

    Pipeline->>S3: Upload checkpoints<br/>PUT /bucket/checkpoints/<br/>AWS IAM
    S3-->>Pipeline: Checkpoint saved

    Pipeline->>ModelReg: Register trained model<br/>POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/<br/>Model metadata + metrics
    ModelReg-->>Pipeline: Model version created

    Note over User,Prometheus: Status Monitoring

    Dashboard->>KServe: Watch InferenceService CRDs
    Dashboard->>DSP: Watch Workflow CRs
    Dashboard->>ModelReg: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/models<br/>List models
    Dashboard-->>User: Display pipeline & model status
